data.description: Come home to this private country setting and feel your day melt away as you sit on the deck and enjoy the view. The huge living room with fireplace, tall vaulted ceiling, with loft area greet you as you enter the house.  A trip down to the basement reveals a huge space plumbed and ready for your ideas and renovations. Single floor living with an open and convenient layout. Make an appointment with Chris Arnold at 570-412-2053 for a private showing. Agents please make showing requests through Showing Time. 24 hours notice is preferred!
